    - [x] Actions column
  - [x] Implement "Create New User" functionality:
    - [x] Add prominent green MUI Button
    - [x] Create dialog with form fields (name, role)
    - [x] Implement client-side validation
    - [x] Add confirmation dialog before submission
  - [x] Add "Edit User" capability:
    - [x] Create dialog with pre-filled fields
    - [x] Add confirmation dialog before saving changes
  - [x] Implement disabled "Delete User" button with tooltip
  - [x] Add safeguards:
    - [x] Prevent admin from changing own role if sole active admin
    - [x] Prevent admin from disabling own account if sole active admin
  - [x] Create backend APIs for user management:
    - [x] GET endpoint to list all users
    - [x] POST endpoint to create new user (with automatic UserSetting creation)
    - [x] PUT endpoint to update user details
  - [x] Integrate with user registration control setting (Story 2.5)
  - [x] Implement UI refresh after operations
  - [x] Add success/error feedback via MUI Snackbar
  - Success criteria: Admins can list, create, and edit users (name, role, status)
  - Dependencies: Story 2.1, Epic 1 (User Schema)

