## Affected Components

- Admin dashboard layout and navigation
- User profile management UI
- Admin user management UI
- Application branding configuration
- System settings management
- Backend APIs for all admin functions
- SystemSetting model for persisting application settings
- Confirmation dialog components for critical actions
- File upload and processing utilities

## Dependencies

- Epic 1 (Authentication, User Schema, Middleware)
- Material UI v6
- File upload handling (formidable)
- Image processing
- Zod for API validation

## Technical Considerations

- Admin routes require strict access control
- File uploads need proper validation and security (type, size, dimensions)
- Avatar and branding images require proper storage strategy (overwriting old files)
- User management must include safeguards (can't remove last admin)
- Settings must be properly persisted and retrieved
- Confirmation dialogs must be implemented for critical actions
- API responses should include proper error handling and validation feedback
- UI should provide clear feedback for async operations (loading, success, error)
- Admin interfaces should be responsive, though primarily focused on desktop/tablet
- SystemSetting model should have a consistent structure for different setting types
- File paths should be stored consistently and accessed efficiently

